  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare cardiac MRI with positron emission tomography (PET)
      with fluorodeoxyglucose (FDG) to determine if cardiac MRI images are as good as, or better,
      than PET with FDG.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
